{
  "stem": "24958.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I thought he's gonna be safer there, but he didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, an old tree, you shouldn't replant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he had to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I don't know when.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't exactly know when he left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He left to Czechoslovakia when he was with his brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then he came to Theresienstadt, which was a concentration camp in-- in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And from there, they shipped him to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there he got finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1939, The war caught us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband was on a contact in Krakow, and all of us, we didn't expect that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When-- when the first bomb was falling, we didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We thought that [INAUDIBLE] something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there was the-- the-- the signal for us to go to shelter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to the shelter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the bombs came down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Krakow was pretty much bombed, and a lot of people left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, they fled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had a little boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My boy was-- oh, it was, he was born in-- four years old, so how far can I go with him?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Money, we didn't have too much either because we used to live very nicely.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My husband made very nice money, but we spended it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I think, where can I go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we stayed on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to go from one ghetto to the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went back to Warsaw, and there we couldn't live anymore in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to get to a section where Jews are concentrated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Before we get there, just tell me a little bit more when-- when the war broke out in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Tell me about that first day and what you remember seeing and hearing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
